-It won't.

20:32.560 --> 20:35.029
(gunshots)

20:36.030 --> 20:38.632
Yeah. There. Take that, lock.

20:40.000 --> 20:41.969
Oh, what the hell, man?

20:42.002 --> 20:43.737
And the door wasn't even locked.

20:43.771 --> 20:44.972
