for that door, Frank.

20:45.005 --> 20:46.540
All right, all right.

20:46.574 --> 20:48.843
Well, this is great.
This is just great.

20:48.876 --> 20:49.977
You know, like, now
what are we supposed to all put

20:50.010 --> 20:51.979
-our teeth in?
-Our faces?

20:52.012 --> 20:53.714
-What are you talking about?
-I'm talking about our legacy.

20:53.747 --> 20:55.549
You know?
I can't hold onto it, man.

20:55.583 --> 20:57.284
Legacy? You want to talk legacy?
You know what our legacy is?

20:57.318 --> 20:58.619
Spending our lives
in this goddamn bar

20:58.652 --> 21:00.821
with a lunatic man
who acts like a dog

21:00.855 --> 21:02.690
