his gun like a maniac!

21:02.723 --> 21:04.558
Oh, fine.

21:04.592 --> 21:07.495
I see where this
pity party's headed.

21:07.528 --> 21:09.563
If you're gonna be
crybabies about it,

21:09.597 --> 21:11.765
all right, take my gun.

21:14.435 --> 21:15.970
-Ow! Ow!
-Shit!

21:16.003 --> 21:17.571
